-- ── brevo → marketing-seo ───────────────────────────────────
('Brevo', 'brevo', 'All-in-one marketing platform — email, SMS, WhatsApp, CRM, automation, transactional email, and meetings under one bill.', 'Brevo (rebranded from Sendinblue in 2023) is a French-founded all-in-one marketing platform that bundles email marketing, SMS, WhatsApp, a built-in CRM, marketing automation, transactional email and SMTP, landing pages, signup forms, and meeting scheduling under one platform. The pricing model differs structurally from most US-based competitors: contacts are unlimited at every tier; you pay only for emails sent, which makes Brevo unusually cheap for email lists with low send frequency (newsletters, monthly broadcasts) and competitive for higher volume too. Marketing automation supports visual workflows with conditional branching; the CRM handles lead capture, deal pipelines, and basic sales tasks; transactional email and SMTP cover developer use cases that compete with Postmark, SendGrid, and Mailgun. Brevo positions against Mailchimp (US incumbent, contact-based pricing), Klaviyo (ecommerce-vertical specialist), ActiveCampaign (deeper automation, US-focused), GetResponse (similar all-in-one positioning), Constant Contact (US SMB legacy), and MailerLite (cheaper but lighter). The differentiator is the unlimited-contacts pricing model + multichannel breadth (email + SMS + WhatsApp + transactional) at SMB price points.', 'https://www.brevo.com', 'freemium', '[{"plan":"Free","price":"$0","features":["Up to 300 emails/day","Unlimited contacts","Drag-and-drop email editor","Mobile-friendly templates","Transactional emails (SMTP)"]},{"plan":"Starter","price":"From $25/mo","features":["Unlimited contacts","From 20K emails/mo","No daily sending limit","No Brevo logo","Basic reporting","Email support"]},{"plan":"Business","price":"From $65/mo","features":["Unlimited contacts","From 20K emails/mo","Marketing automation","Landing pages","A/B testing","Multi-user access","Advanced reporting"]},{"plan":"BrevoPlus","price":"Custom (Enterprise)","features":["Custom volume","SSO + advanced security","Sub-account management","SLA","Dedicated CSM","Tailored onboarding"]}]'::jsonb, 'beginner', true, '{"web","api","mobile"}', '{"Email marketing with unlimited contacts","SMS marketing campaigns","WhatsApp Business API messaging","Built-in CRM with deal pipelines","Marketing automation with visual workflows","Transactional email + SMTP API","Landing pages and signup forms","Meeting scheduling tool","Multi-user access (Business+)","A/B testing + advanced reporting","Multi-language support","GDPR-compliant (EU-headquartered)"}', '{"Shopify","WooCommerce","Salesforce","HubSpot","Zapier","Make","WordPress","Stripe","PayPal","Magento","BigCommerce","Microsoft Dynamics 365"}', true, '{"SMBs needing email + SMS + WhatsApp under one bill at SMB pricing","Newsletter operators with large lists but low send frequency (unlimited contacts wins)","EU-based businesses needing GDPR-native infrastructure","Developers needing transactional SMTP alongside marketing email"}', '{"DTC ecommerce wanting Klaviyo-grade segmentation depth (Klaviyo wins)","Enterprise B2B sales needing a real CRM (Salesforce / HubSpot fit)","Pure transactional email shops at scale (Postmark / SendGrid often cheaper at volume)","Teams wanting deepest US-style automation visual builder (ActiveCampaign deeper)"}', 'The most cost-efficient all-in-one marketing platform for SMBs in 2026 — Brevo''s unlimited-contacts pricing model means newsletter operators pay 50-80% less than Mailchimp at equivalent list sizes, and the bundled SMS + WhatsApp + transactional makes it a real consolidation play. EU-headquartered and GDPR-native is a real plus for European operators. It''s weaker than Klaviyo on ecommerce-specific segmentation, weaker than ActiveCampaign on automation depth, and the visual builder UI is functional but a step behind US-built competitors. Pick Brevo when budget + multichannel matter more than best-in-class polish.', now()),

-- ── drip → marketing-seo ────────────────────────────────────
('Drip', 'drip', 'Ecommerce email and SMS marketing automation for DTC brands — visual workflows, dynamic segmentation, and behavioral targeting.', 'Drip is an email and SMS marketing automation platform built specifically for DTC ecommerce brands and online educators. The product is positioned as the mid-market alternative to Klaviyo: similar ecommerce-vertical focus and behavioral segmentation depth, but at a lower entry price and with a more accessible visual workflow builder. Visual Email Builder lets non-developers design and send; Dynamic Segmentation auto-groups audiences by behavior (browse, cart, purchase) and lifecycle stage; Personalization Engine inserts real customer data into messages; pre-built workflow templates cover browse abandonment, onboarding, and event reminders out of the box; Onsite Pop-ups capture attention and conversion-fire directly on the storefront; Insights and Reporting track customer-story journeys and campaign performance. Subscriber-based pricing scales with active contact count and monthly email volume; enterprise migration support kicks in past 17,500 contacts. Drip positions against Klaviyo (ecommerce-vertical incumbent, broader feature surface and higher price), Mailchimp (legacy SMB email), ActiveCampaign (B2B-leaning automation), Omnisend (SMS-first ecommerce), Postscript (SMS-only specialist), and Yotpo Email (reviews + email bundle).', 'https://www.drip.com', 'paid', '[]'::jsonb, 'intermediate', true, '{"web","api"}', '{"Visual Email Builder for non-developers","Dynamic Segmentation by behavior + lifecycle stage","Personalization Engine with customer-data insertion","Pre-built workflow templates (browse abandonment, onboarding)","Onsite Pop-ups for storefront conversion capture","Insights + customer-story journey tracking","SMS marketing automation","50+ ecommerce + tooling integrations","Enterprise migration support past 17,500 contacts","Subscriber-based pricing"}', '{"Shopify","Shopify Plus","WooCommerce","BigCommerce","Stripe","Facebook Custom Audiences","Typeform","Zapier","Magento","Klaviyo (migration)"}', true, '{"DTC ecommerce brands on Shopify or WooCommerce running behavioral email","Mid-market merchants priced out of Klaviyo but needing more than Mailchimp","Online educators selling courses with behavioral lifecycle automation","Brands wanting bundled email + SMS + onsite pop-ups in one platform"}', '{"B2B sales teams needing a real CRM + sequencing (use HubSpot / Outreach)","Enterprise ecommerce committed to Klaviyo (switching cost outweighs savings)","Pure transactional email use cases (Postmark / SendGrid cheaper)","Newsletter creators with no ecommerce store (use Beehiiv or Kit)"}', 'A solid mid-market alternative to Klaviyo for DTC ecommerce brands in 2026 — Drip delivers the same visual-workflow + behavioral-segmentation pattern at a more accessible entry price, and the pre-built templates ship usable browse-abandonment + onboarding flows in hours. It''s weaker than Klaviyo on ecommerce-specific feature depth and the broader integration ecosystem, weaker than Omnisend on SMS-first workflows, and the no-public-pricing tier table is friction. Pick Drip when you''re a Shopify or WooCommerce brand priced out of Klaviyo; skip if you''ve already invested in Klaviyo''s ecosystem.', now()),

-- ── aweber → marketing-seo ──────────────────────────────────
('AWeber', 'aweber', 'Email marketing for small businesses and creators — drag-and-drop builder, AI subject-line writer, automation, landing pages, and 750+ integrations.', 'AWeber is one of the original email marketing platforms (founded 1998) that has steadily added AI and creator-economy features while staying focused on small businesses and content creators rather than enterprise or ecommerce-vertical motion. The 2024–2026 product covers a drag-and-drop email builder with mobile-friendly templates, marketing automation with 90% pre-built workflows you customize and activate, landing page builder with ready-made templates, AI Writing & Subject Line Assistant for first-draft email copy and subject testing, ecommerce integration with online-store setup in minutes, web push notifications, abandoned-cart and upsell automations, and a 14-day free trial. Pricing tiers cover Free (limited features), Lite from $15/mo, Plus from $30/mo, and Done For You at $30/mo + $79 one-time setup. AWeber''s integration breadth is the headline number: 750+ tools including WordPress, Shopify, PayPal, Zapier, Facebook, and Stripe. Positions against Mailchimp (broader SMB incumbent), ConvertKit / Kit (creator-economy specialist with deeper sequence automation), MailerLite (cheaper, lighter), GetResponse (similar all-in-one), and Constant Contact (US SMB legacy).', 'https://www.aweber.com', 'freemium', '[{"plan":"Free","price":"$0 (limited)","features":["Up to 500 subscribers","One landing page","Basic email automation","Up to 3,000 emails/mo"]},{"plan":"Lite","price":"From $15/mo","features":["Unlimited email lists","Unlimited landing pages","Unlimited automations","Removes AWeber branding","Basic reporting","AI writing assistant"]},{"plan":"Plus","price":"From $30/mo","features":["Multiple users","Behavioral segmentation","Advanced reporting","Sales tracking","Priority support","All Lite features"]},{"plan":"Done For You","price":"$30/mo + $79 one-time setup","features":["Account setup by AWeber team","Custom workflow build-out","Branded template setup","Training included"]}]'::jsonb, 'beginner', true, '{"web","mobile","api"}', '{"Drag-and-drop email builder","Marketing automation (90%+ pre-built templates)","Landing page builder","AI Writing + Subject Line Assistant","Ecommerce store integration (set up in minutes)","Web push notifications","Pre-built abandoned-cart + upsell automations","750+ tool integrations","Free 14-day trial","Comparison-page library vs Mailchimp / ConvertKit / GetResponse / Constant Contact"}', '{"WordPress","Shopify","PayPal","Stripe","Zapier","Facebook","ClickFunnels","WooCommerce","Etsy","Squarespace"}', true, '{"Small businesses and solopreneurs running newsletters and basic automation","Creators on a budget needing AI subject lines + drag-and-drop without ConvertKit/Kit pricing","WordPress + Shopify operators wanting wide integration ecosystem","Buyers wanting a Done-For-You setup option (rare in this category)"}', '{"DTC ecommerce brands needing Klaviyo-grade segmentation","Newsletter creators monetizing paid subs (Beehiiv / Kit fit much better)","Enterprise B2B teams (HubSpot / Salesforce Marketing Cloud fit)","Buyers needing best-in-class AI writing depth (Jasper / Copy.ai dedicated)"}', 'A solid value pick for small-business email marketing in 2026 — AWeber bundles drag-and-drop, automation, landing pages, AI subject lines, and 750+ integrations at $15/mo entry, materially cheaper than Mailchimp''s equivalent tier with comparable feature surface. The Done For You tier ($30/mo + $79 setup) is genuinely useful for non-technical operators who want hands-off launch. It''s weaker than ConvertKit / Kit on creator-economy primitives (paid subs, Creator Network), weaker than Klaviyo on ecommerce automation depth, and the brand reads "legacy" vs newer entrants. Pick AWeber when budget + ease of use matter more than category-specific depth.', now())

ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;

INSERT INTO tool_categories (tool_id, category_id)
SELECT t.id, c.id FROM tools t JOIN categories c ON c.slug = 'marketing-seo' WHERE t.slug = 'brevo'  ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
